{"tid":2400591,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票唔係賭馬賭波，無人催你架，慢慢黎啦","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T06:16:20.000Z","uid":109573,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"98001501d504d4e7bbc0aa1a1d7347f197cd698a","tid":2400591,"uid":109573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"單純發表下個人感受。<br />\n<br />\n黎咗連登財經台唔經唔覺己經就五年，<br />\n<br />\n我發現最近大家既post既風氣由最初偏向輕鬆氛圍既講笑/學術討論post，變到而家差唔多每個討論post入面都有回覆&ldquo;跟！&ldquo;，&ldquo;信你&rdquo;，&ldquo;入咗先&ldquo;。。。<br />\n<br />\n無可否認，財經台好多好叻投資既巴絲打，佢地亦都好樂意分享自己倉位資訊比大家。但係唔代表大家應該無思考直接跟注。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大到買車買樓，下到買傢俬電器，我相信大部人買野之前都會做足research，格好晒價先出手，何解去到股票大家就變咗衝衝衝呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買賣股票，起碼要對目標股票自己有一定既見解，佢係市場度咩地位，有咩競爭對手，相比之下有咩優勢。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一味跟機，最後賺到既遲早會還返出去。 miss咗個升浪，咪再下個囉，人一日唔死一日都仲有得買賣股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢學，慢慢買，股票絕非賭場賭錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> <span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n如<br />\n日<br />\n中<br />\n天<br />\n教<br />\n！</span> </span>"},{"pid":"7dd948f8295a23ccaedb101a7baa47b8ca7a5d60","tid":2400591,"uid":9974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"大龍市日日爆升 買遲半秒都跑輸其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲慢慢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aea2679318182941fc2d7287deba15aaa938570","tid":2400591,"uid":109573,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7dd948f8295a23ccaedb101a7baa47b8ca7a5d60","tid":2400591,"uid":9974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"大龍市日日爆升 買遲